Blockchain boosts commodity trading and financing

   The digitisation of international trade is stepping up a gear thanks to
   Blockchain technology. The projects led by Societe Generale and its
   European partners are at the forefront of this shift. We take a closer
   look at this new technology and its numerous impacts on trading and
   financing.

   Find out more about Blockchain

