     * Partager sur LinkedIn

New technologies for stronger cybersecurity

   Digital accounts for 86% of our incoming contacts, with 700 million
   logins per year, mostly from mobile devices. Mobile has been the
   most-used medium since the end of 2012. This profound change in the
   bank’s customer relations has heightened the security challenge, which
   Societe Generale will address by more than doubling its IT budget for
   cybersecurity and investing in new technologies.

   Read the article

     * Read the article of Thierry Olivier on Linkedin

