     * Partager sur LinkedIn

Data, a strategic asset for Societe Generale

   Today, data is central to customer relations and the Societe Generale
   Group organisation. In a digital environment, the Bank improves its
   services to its clients, its risk management, and its operational
   efficiency, thanks to data use while ensuring its quality, security and
   protection.

   Read our feature on the data

