Open source development to encourage innovation

   As the embodiment of collective intelligence, open source development
   is an important driver of innovation for Societe Generale's information
   systems. It is a strategic commitment that has already produced
   results, as 80% of the Group's development technologies are open
   source. Use, Contribute and Attract: learn about the three components
   of Societe Generale's open source strategy.

   Find out more

