Hackathons reinventing the bank

   Aiming for strength in numbers, Societe Generale is pursuing the
   development of its open innovation system and extending its reach to
   partner communities and their creativity. In this spirit, the bank has
   organised hackathons and challenges in order to identify projects with
   the potential to reinvent banking relations for the digital age and
   successfully transform the company.

   Find out more

