The Tech culture within Societe Generale

   New technologies are an opportunity to invent new banking solutions and
   continuously improve the client experience. Innovating on a daily basis
   is part of Societe Generale’s DNA, and that’s why the Bank is looking
   for diverse profiles who are ready to become involved in major projects
   and missions. Staff members who work in IT jobs have their say.

   IT jobs at Societe Generale

