Developping the digital transformation with leading tech influencers

   In October 2018, Societe Generale’s senior management joined the heads
   of the Group's IT infrastructure for their first External Advisory
   Board meeting with 10 leading tech influencers to discuss and enhance
   digital strategy issues, new market trends and how to further
   accelerate the Group’s digital transformation. Influencers present
   included Scott Guthrie, Executive Vice President of Microsoft, Steve
   Singh, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Docker and Octave Klaba,
   Chairman and founder of OVH. The topics covered included Cloud, Open
   Source, Big Data & AI and the Digital Workplace.

