   Carlos Goncalvès

Unity is strength

   In a world that is evolving faster and faster, we cannot answer the
   technological challenges we are facing without opening up and sharing
   these challenges with the tech and innovation ecosystem.
   How can we make the IT Infrastructure more flexible and agile while
   ensuring security and complying with regulations? How can we integrate
   emerging technologies (5G, cognitive services, etc.) in our strategy
   and better anticipate new uses? How can we improve user experience and
   make it simpler and smoother?

   Read Carlos Goncalvès' article on Linkedin

